<ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4">
  <li><strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Step 1:</strong> Pick your grading scale from the dropdown. Your options are: 4.0 Scale (US Standard), 4.3 Scale (US with A+), 5.0 Scale (International), or 10.0 Scale (India/Pakistan). Pick the wrong one and your GPA won't mean much, so double-check what your school uses.</li>
