<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">This is the one students pull up most often right before finals. It works backward from the grade you <strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">want</strong> to tell you the score you <strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">need</strong>.</p>
<ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4">
