  <li><strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Step 2:</strong> Enter the Weight Already Completed (%) &mdash; the total percentage of your course grade that has already been graded. If your homework (20%), quizzes (20%), and midterm (20%) are all done, you'd type 60 here.</li>
  <li><strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Step 3:</strong> Put in your Target Final Grade (%) &mdash; the grade you're hoping to finish with.</li>
